headline: Revisiting State Street (STT) Valuation After Its Recent Share Price Strength
summary: State Street (STT) has been quietly rewarding patient investors, with the stock up about 8% over the past 3 months and roughly 28% over the past year, outpacing many traditional financial peers. See our latest analysis for State Street. That steady climb in State Street’s share price, now at $121.87, reflects investors warming to its improving fundamentals, with a strong year to date share price return helping reinforce an already powerful multi year total shareholder return story.
